_sText: In this map you'll find places to get weapons with ammo. You can get the AWP when you jump very far! With the high speed you have from surfing, you'll get enough speed to jump over the hole. This will need some practising, but it's possible! This method is UNIQUE and never used in any surf map i've seen! But, if you fall somewhere in the map, you'll get teleported to the jail! You can escape by yourself to jump over some blocks to hit the button! You can also find some he grenades and the Ak47 at the top and you can find the m4a1 at the jail. I hope you enjoy!
